comments: Plumlee (DET) is drawn into the air by the pump fake from Theis (BOS) and on his way down he makes contact to Theis' (BOS) body during his shooting motion.
Mykhailiuk (DET) makes marginal contact to Brown's (BOS) body at the start of the drive, before he cleanly dislodges the ball out of bounds.
Smart (BOS) briefly places his forearm to the front of Rose (DET) during the drive up the court. The contact is marginal.
Grant (DET) ends his dribble and hops consecutively on the same foot after his gather.
Thompson (BOS) does not establish himself in the path of Mykhailiuk (DET) while setting the screen, and delivers contact to his back while he is trying to defend around the screen.
Thompson (BOS) makes contact to Griffin's (DET) arm during his shooting motion that disrupts his layup attempt.
Tatum (BOS) releases and does not extend his off arm elbow to wrist into Grant's body at the end of his drive to the basket.
Theis (BOS) makes contact to Plumlee's (DET) arm as he gathers and enters his shooting motion, during the driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) makes marginal contact to Rose's (DET) body as he gathers and enters  shooting motion. Rose is able to move through the contact and it does not disrupt his ability to attempt the layup.
Oljeleye (BOS) goes to but not through the screen set by Griffin (DET). Griffin's reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Ojeleye (BOS) makes contact to Grant's (DET) body on the drive that disrupts his SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Griffin (DET) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
